nicer error message for multiply defined config

Original error is displayed. Now looks like:

Error loading argument App.opt=['1', '2'], opt only accepts one value, got 2: ['1', '2']
expand documentation of from_string and related CLI changes

do not print help on error

help output is super long and includes all options,
which is too much output and can hide the error.

With argparse, invalid/unrecognized args get better error messages now,
so I don't think this is helpful anymore.
